PC -> Arduino:

|<---mode----->||<----speed--->||<-----------steps------------>| 
[][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][]
7 6 5 4 3 2 1 0	    

mode bits layout:
bit 0 :	1 : CW, 0 : CCW
bit 1 : undefined
bit 2 : undefined
bit 3 : undefined
bit 4 : 1 : uStep
bit 5 : 1 : hStep
bit 6 : 1 : fStep
bit 7 : 1 : wave


	  
